ISLAMABAD, Jun 17 (APP): Federal Minister for Interior Mohsin Naqvi expressed deep sorrow over the martyrdom of five policemen in a traffic accident near Lasbela late Sunday night.
Naqvi expressed his heartfelt sympathy and condolences to the families of the martyrs, said the press note. He prayed for the speedy recovery of the injured police personnel.
